# Triple License

Copyright 2024-2026 Ilya Selyutin, Nikolai Kovalev and contributors

This work is available under three licenses. Choose the one that fits your use case.

---

## 1. Apache-2.0-NC (Non-Commercial)

**Free** for research, education, and personal use.

- Academic and scientific research
- Personal projects (non-revenue)
- Educational purposes
- Evaluation and prototyping

See [LICENSE-APACHE-NC.md](./LICENSE-APACHE-NC.md)

---

## 2. AGPL-3.0 (Open-Source Copyleft)

**Free** for open-source projects with copyleft obligation.

- Commercial use allowed if your project is fully open-source under AGPL-3.0
- Network use triggers source disclosure (if you run a modified version as a service, you must release source)
- All derivative works must remain AGPL-3.0

See [LICENSE-AGPL.md](./LICENSE-AGPL.md)

---

## 3. Commercial License (Proprietary)

**Paid** license for proprietary / closed-source / commercial use.

- Closed-source integration
- SaaS / API offerings
- No copyleft obligations
- Priority support available

See [LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md](./LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md)

Contact: psy.seliger@yandex.ru / comonoid@yandex.ru

---

## Quick Selection Guide

| Your Use Case | License | Cost |
|---------------|---------|------|
| Research / Education / Personal | Apache-2.0-NC | Free |
| Open-source project (copyleft OK) | AGPL-3.0 | Free |
| Proprietary / Commercial / SaaS | Commercial | Paid |

---

